snippet.title: Amber Theoharis Reveals She Almost Gave Birth On NFL Total Access Set & Talks Her WinQuik Trivia App
snippet.description:
Former host of NFL Total Access, Amber Theoharis, tells Julie Steart-Binks that after she had her baby, she rushed back to her job, only to find out she had been replaced. She also talks about her current job at WinQuik Trivia App. Watch “Drinks with Binks” every Wednesday night at 8pm ET / PT on fuboTV or stream it FREE at fubosportsnetwork.com
